data.description: Charming 1938 sq ft Townhouse- Prime Location. Step into this meticulously maintained townhouse boasting a spacious space, perfectly designed to cater to modern lifestyles. This home showcases three generously sized bedrooms and 2.5 pristine baths, ensuring comfort and convenience for every resident. The kitchen, a cook's dream is equipped with state-of-the- art newer appliances, providing an inviting space for culinary exploration and memorable family meals. Central air conditioning, in 2018, ensures year-round comfort,making both hot summers and chilly winters a breeze. Attention to detail is evident in numerous updates gracing both the exterior and interior of this residence. The chic designed and contemporary finishes echo sophisticated living,blending seamlessly with functional spaces. One of many highlights of this home's enviable location is its proximity to leisure and entertainment. It's just a short stroll away from the clubhouse, perfect for afternoon get togethers or weekend relaxation. Moreover, a mere minutes drive will land you amidst a bustling hub of shopping and restaurants, offering a mix of local boutiques and gourmet dining options. Discover the blend of urban convenience and modern luxury in the stunning townhouse, ready to be called your new home.
